profile_positions.description:
Delivered various IT consultancy assignments as Senior Manager, including a strategy for the IT landscape of a healthcare institution after an M&A.

Promoted Ventus through exhibition and customer visits and delivered various assignments including:
• A strategy report for Ventus' Social Media;
• A research report on current and new technologies for a program at the Ventus Academy;
• A research report, search profiles and a learning trajectory for Young Professionals aimed at their recruitment and growth opportunities in competencies and skills.

Analyzed and rewrote internal job profiles, helped colleagues by reviewing their resumes and motivational letters and wrote IT related articles for the Ventus website.

Managing Consultant for the Program Office ERP at the Defense Material Organization (DMO). Responsible for guiding the migration from IT legacy systems to SAP BW ERP software for the Royal Navy. My tasks included:

• Consulting stakeholders and Steering Committee regarding all Navy migration projects with a key focus on planning, finance, data quality and business requirements;
• Organizing and leading evaluation meetings to determine the dates to and achieve Go Lives;
• Developing and testing guidelines (planning, finance, data quality and business requirements) for Business units;
• Monitoring quality based on the in-company framework Result-oriented work 2.1.
• Addressing and advising on project issues as a member of the Steering Committee Project Assurance and Support on a C-level with Generals and Colonels.

• Achieved successful Go-lives for 4 out of 8 projects within 18 months.

Recruited by Content Staffing and Recruitment (now known as Unique - Staffing and Recruiting) and employed by DTO (IT organisation and datacenter of the Dutch Ministry of Defence). Responsible for:

• Developing CMS (Content Management Systems) templates with HTML, Perl, CSS, ASP and Vbscript;
• Supporting the Customer service of the Service Desk;
• Providing technical support and incident handling for all CMS (Smartsite and TDS Tridion).
